    "description": "Microsatellite instability detection using cfDNA sequencing data.\n\nMSIsensor-ct is a novel method based machine learning, which can accurately determine the MSI status of cfDNA sequencing data with ultra-low ctDNA content. In practice, we recommend aiming for a minimum of 30 valid microsatellites to classify the MSI status using MSIsensor-ct. MSIsensor (https://github.com/niu-lab/msisensor) is a viable option if paired tumor and normal sequencing data are available, and MSIsensor2 (https://github.com/niu-lab/msisensor2) is effective for tumor-only samples.",
